[ ITEM NOTES ]

Only a few items are currently implemented in the current prototype.
Some are fully functional.
Some are reward / progression items.
Some are placeholders for future floors.

Combat-related item behavior currently exists for:
    * Stick
    * Torch
    * Small Potion

Non-combat / progression items currently include:
    * Iron Key
    * Ancient Relic
    * Gold


